      Hints And Tips For Playing Video Clips
      --------------------------------------

To play the video clips in this directory smoothly
with best results on an A7000 or Risc PC without
video memory, choose the following:

Screen mode - Use the !ARPlayer 'Play big' button 
              to play the video full-screen, or 
              choose a screen mode such as
              640 x 480, 256 colours before playing.

!ARPlayer   - Ensure that you do NOT use the 
 choices      'Interpolate' option on the !ARPlayer
              Global choices dialogue box.

Video clips - Use the video clips in this directory, 
              NOT those in the HiRes subdirectory.
                    
For more details, see the ReadMe file in this
directory.
